<div class="h-news">
<div class="h-title">
中国旅游龙头与船舶巨头将全面合作挺进邮轮产业
</div>
<div class="h-info">
<span class="h-time"> 2017-03-31 15:09:20</span>
<span>
来源：
<em id="source"> 新华网</em>
</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="main">
<div class="part part1 clearfix" id="">
<div class="fllow1-wap left">
<div class="p-left left" id="fllow1">
<div class="s-ewm">
