ws.cn/nc/1-1120732835.html" class="detail-amount" target="_blank">（评论<b>1</b>条&nbsp;查看全部&gt;&gt;）</a></span></h2></div><div id="JFO_REMOTE_65809_1491074818231dl-section" class="dl-section clearfix"><dl class="clearfix t-1"><dt><div class="ds-pic"><a href="http://122739493.home.news.cn/" target="_blank"><img src="http://comment.home.news.cn/images/icon_39x39.gif" alt="" data-url="http://tpic.home.news.cn/userIcon/s/122739493"></a></div><div class="ds-watch"><a href="javascript:;" data-watch="122739493"><strong>+</strong>关注</a></div></dt><dd style="width: 594px; "><h3 class="ds-nick"><a href="http://122739493.home.news.cn/" target="_blank">比肩而事5067847</a>&nbsp;<em>[中国广东省深圳市 <a href="http://www.xinhuanet.com/" target="_blank"></a>]</em>：<em class="ds-time" data-timestamp="1490971588000">03月31日 22:46 发表</em></h3><p class="ds-text"><em class="ds-content" id="COM_1841185_content">中国旅游巨头对产业发展滞后、迟钝。错过很多时代机遇</em></p><h4 class="ds-ctrl"><a href="javascript:;" class="ding" data-cid="1841185" data-uid="122739493">顶<span>(<em>0</em>)</span></a><a href="javascript:;" class="reply" data-id="1841185">回复</a><a href="javascript:;" class="copy">复制</a><a href="javascript:;" class="report" data-cid="1841185" data-uid="122739493" data-uname="比肩而事5067847">举报</a></h4></dd></dl><div class="line-break-dashed t-1">&nbsp;</div><div class="more"><a href="http://comment.home.news.cn/nc/1-1120732835.html" data-time="1" data-cur="1" class="submit" target="_blank">显示更多评论</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="http://comment.home.news.cn/" target="_blank">新闻留言排行榜</a></div></div></div></div></div>
